Package com.example.cmput301f24mikasa

Class Notifications

java.lang.Object
com.example.cmput301f24mikasa.Notifications
public class Notifications extends Object
Represents a notification sent to a user related to an event. Contains information about the notification text, sender, recipient, and associated event details.
